verse_part: there is among you of all
be with him! Let him go
but they could not be located
to them that they should not eat
on it, as it is written
with you, for we, like you, seek
in common with us in building
to him in which it was written
you, and that we might write
and it is not yet completed
to you and to your brothers
of you, it shall be done
that there will not be wrath
you that it is not allowed
and with them were the Levites
as wives for themselves and for their sons
and on account of our iniquities
but we will be with you; be courageous
households for each of their father's
